# Implementation Orchestration (App Only)

**App-only**: This rule applies only when working in the ClaimStation app (`claimstation-app`). Ignore it when working in claimstation-www or other directories.

## At Session Start

1. Read `claimstation-app/docs/en/tech/implementation-status/index.md` for current progress.
2. Identify next task (first unchecked item); check prerequisites; implement; update status.

## Task Completion Checklist

Before marking a task complete: `npm run type-check`, `npm run lint`, `npm run test` in claimstation-app; follow `.cursor/rules/`; use types from `claimstation-app/src/types/` and Supabase from `claimstation-app/src/lib/supabase/`; commit, push, run `gh run watch --exit-status`.

## Post-Change

Consider: version bump (see versioning.mdc), docs in `claimstation-app/docs/`, in-app Help/About, unit and E2E tests. Use Conventional Commits.

